---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Sidebar from '../components/Sidebar.astro';
const nowItems = [
    { text: "Co-organizing GÆMZ Meetup Toyko", link: "https://gaemz.carrd.co/"},
    { text: "Working on TO:RI", link: "https://store.steampowered.com/app/3215280/TORI/"},
    { text: "Reading The Infinite Playground", link: "https://direct.mit.edu/books/book/4846/The-Infinite-PlaygroundA-Player-s-Guide-to"},
    { text: "Learning Blender", link: ""},
    { text: "Working on highway::ephemera", link: ""}
];
---

<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <BaseHead title="Farfama" description="Farfama" />
        <style>
            body {
                font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
                margin: 0;
                padding: 0;
                display: flex;
                font-size: 14px;
                line-height: 1.6;
                color: #333;
                min-height: 100vh;
            }

            .now-section {
                margin-top: 25px;
            }

            .content {
                flex-grow: 1;
                padding: 60px;
                max-width: 800px;
                display: flex;
                gap: 40px;
            }

            .profile-image-container {
                flex-shrink: 0;
                width: 300px;
            }

            .profile-image {
                max-width: 100%;
                height: auto;
                display: block;
            }

            .text-content {
                flex-grow: 1;
            }

            p {
                margin: 0;
            }

            @media (max-width: 768px) {
                body {
                    flex-direction: column;
                }
                .content {
                    flex-direction: column;
                    padding: 20px;
                }
                .profile-image-container {
                    width: 100%;
                    max-width: 300px;
                    margin-bottom: 20px;
                }
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <Sidebar />
        <div class="content">
            <div class="profile-image-container">
                <img src="/profile-photo.jpg" alt="Farfama" class="profile-image">
            </div>
            <div class="text-content">
                <p>Farfama is a media artist currently based in Japan, specializing in experimental digital games and web applications. His work explores themes of awe, wonder, and playful joy, drawing inspiration from nature, ritual, and everyday observation.</p>
                <br>
                <p>Farfamaは日本を拠点に活動するメディアアーティストで、実験的なデジタルゲームやウェブアプリを専門としている。彼らの作品は、自然、儀式、日常的な観察からインスピレーションを得て、畏怖、驚き、遊び心のある喜びというテーマを探求している。</p>

                <br>

                <p> <strong>Exhibitions</strong> </p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Operator Digitalfest (Taiwan) - 2026</li>
                    <li>A MAZE. Berlin Open Screens (Germany) - 2025</li>
                    <li>Avant Beetle CRTL-ALT-RESIST (USA) - 2025</li>
                    <li>The Zium Exposition (Online) - 2025</li>
                    <li>Super FESTival (Canada) - 2024</li>
                    <li>030 Tokyo Microflora Exhibition (Japan) - 2024</li>
                    <li>BLON Animation and Games Festival (Lithuania) - 2024</li>
                    <li>Playtest Kyoto (Japan) - 2024</li>
                    <li>Games Y'all Austin Texas (USA) - 2024</li>
                    <li>Space Orbit Art Gallery Live Performance (Japan) - 2024</li>
                    <li>Dizzy Spell “Short and Sweet” Game Exhibition (USA) - 2023</li>
                </ul>
                <strong>Talks</strong>
                <ul>
                    <li>Games Art International Assembly - 2025</li>
                    <li>Game Devs of Color Expo - 2025</li>
                    <li>Spectrum Tokyo - 2025</li>
                    <li>Tokyo GÆMZ Show - 2025</li>
                    <li>A MAZE Berlin. - 2025</li>
                    <li>GÆMZ Tokyo - 2024</li>
                    <li>Super FESTival - 2024</li>
                </ul>
                <p> <strong>Workshops & Events</strong> </p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Tokyo GÆMZ Show - 2025</li>
                    <li>GÆMZ Tokyo Game Boy Camera Photowalk - 2025</li>
                    <li>Kizuna Collective Mindful Walking Circle - 2025</li>  
                </ul>                  
                <div class="now-section">
                    <strong><p> What I'm up to now</p> </strong>
                    <ul>
                        {nowItems.map((item) => (
                            <li>
                                {item.link ? (
                                    <a href={item.link}>{item.text}</a>
                                ) : (
                                    <span>{item.text}</span>
                                )}
                            </li>
                        ))}
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <br>
                    <p>Contact me at <strong>farfama.dev@gmail.com</strong></p>
                    <p>Follow me on bluesky <a href="https://bsky.app/profile/farfama.bsky.social">@farfama</p></a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>
